import { Flex, Spacer, Center, Box, Text, Square } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import '../index.css'

const heading = {
  fontSize: 32,
  fontWeight: 700,
  textAlign: 'left' as const,
  color: ('#22223B'),
  textShadow: '-2px 2px 2px #4A4E69',
}

export default function Heading() {
  return (
    <Flex >
      <Box w='50%' className='name'>
        <Text {...heading} >Ari Wisenburn</Text>
      </Box>
      <Box flex='1'>
        <Text>Box 3</Text>
      </Box>
    </Flex >
  )
}
